{
  "score": {
    "overall": 85,
    "dimensions": [
      { "key": "goalAchievement", "label": "Goal Achievement", "score": 90 },
      { "key": "outputQuality", "label": "Output Quality", "score": 85 },
      { "key": "constraintCompliance", "label": "Constraint Compliance", "score": 80 },
      { "key": "promptEffectiveness", "label": "Prompt Effectiveness", "score": 85 }
    ]
  },
  "improvements": [
    "Add explicit guidance on document structure and formatting to ensure consistency across different document types.",
    "Specify that the output should avoid placeholder text like 'YYYY年MM月DD日' and use realistic or generic dates.",
    "Clarify that the document should directly address the target user's needs without unnecessary boilerplate sections."
  ],
  "patchPlan": [
    {
      "op": "replace",
      "oldText": "**输出要求：**\n1.  请生成一份完整的、可直接使用的文档。\n2.  文档的结构、格式、语言风格和详细程度应严格匹配上述“文档类型”和“目标用户”的需求。\n3.  文档内容必须完全满足“质量要求”中列出的所有标准。\n4.  最终输出应为文档的完整内容，无需额外解释或说明。",
      "newText": "**输出要求：**\n1.  请生成一份完整的、可直接使用的文档，避免使用未填充的占位符（如日期、姓名）。\n2.  文档的结构、格式、语言风格和详细程度应严格匹配上述“文档类型”和“目标用户”的需求，优先采用行业标准或常见模板。\n3.  文档内容必须完全满足“质量要求”中列出的所有标准，并聚焦于核心信息，避免冗余部分。\n4.  最终输出应为文档的完整内容，无需额外解释或说明。",
      "instruction": "The output used placeholder dates and included boilerplate sections. This patch adds explicit guidance to avoid placeholders and prioritize concise, user-focused content."
    }
  ],
  "summary": "The prompt effectively guided the generation of a professional weekly report, but minor improvements in formatting and content focus are needed."
}

